snippet: Justin Ruggiano, Mike Olt and Welington Castillo hit two-run homers to power the Chicago Cubs to a 16-9 victory over the Boston Red Sox on Wednesday night, completing a three-game interleague series sweep....

headline.print_headline: Cubs Complete Sweep Over Red Sox, 16-9
headline.main: Cubs Complete Sweep Over Red Sox, 16-9

lead_paragraph: Justin Ruggiano, Mike Olt and Welington Castillo hit two-run homers to power the Chicago Cubs to a 16-9 victory over the Boston Red Sox on Wednesday night, completing a three-game interleague series sweep.
